Package base_SOM_Objects.som_segments

Class SOM_MapNodeClassSegMgr

java.lang.Object
base_SOM_Objects.som_segments.SOM_MapNodeSegMgr
base_SOM_Objects.som_segments.SOM_MapNodeClassSegMgr
public class SOM_MapNodeClassSegMgr extends SOM_MapNodeSegMgr
This class manages all of a single map node's class-type segment functionality. A class-type segment means the segment is built upon degrees of membership to a particular shared class by the examples that map to the owning map node.

john
